title: ZBT #103: Boot Camp 101
description:
We at Zero Blog Thirty have been through it all (expcept PFC Bren). So we want to teach you how to get through every facet of your military career. On today's episode, we answer questions from those of you who are going through the motions at boot camp. You won't find better military advice anywhere.
